      <title>拜登获得足够的代表赢得 2024 年民主党提名</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-13/biden-gets-enough-delegates-to-win-2024-democratic-nomination</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据美联社报道，总统乔·拜登周二赢得了足够的代表票，以确保获得民主党总统提名。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-13/biden-gets-enough-delegates-to-win-2024-democratic-nomination</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 13 Mar 2024 00:12:37 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>杜达希望波兰为第二座核电站选择美国投资者</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-12/poland-s-duda-wants-us-to-build-its-second-nuclear-power-plant</link>
      <description><![CDATA[总统安杰伊·杜达表示，波兰应该为其第二座核电站选择美国投资者，这可能会让他与似乎倾向于将投资移交给法国的政府产生分歧。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-12/poland-s-duda-wants-us-to-build-its-second-nuclear-power-plant</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 12 Mar 2024 22:46:08 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Milei 获胜，阿根廷完成 500 亿美元债务互换</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-12/argentina-swaps-50-billion-of-local-debt-to-push-out-repayments</link>
      <description><![CDATA[阿根廷成功地将今年到期的约 77% 比索债务换成较长期票据，这为哈维尔·米莱总统赢得了胜利，因为他积极采取行动支撑公共财政并稳定容易发生危机的经济。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-12/argentina-swaps-50-billion-of-local-debt-to-push-out-repayments</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 12 Mar 2024 22:44:26 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>部长称巴西计划救助陷入困境的农业部门</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-12/brazil-plans-rescue-for-troubled-farming-sector-minister-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[巴西政府正在为因玉米和大豆价格暴跌而陷入违约的农民和因拖欠债务而苦苦挣扎的农业公司制定救助计划。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-12/brazil-plans-rescue-for-troubled-farming-sector-minister-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 12 Mar 2024 22:27:56 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>波兰总统杜达警告称，如果俄罗斯在乌克兰获胜，普京将攻击其他国家</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-12/duda-warns-putin-will-attack-others-if-russia-wins-in-ukraine</link>
      <description><![CDATA[波兰总统安杰伊·杜达表示，如果克里姆林宫赢得乌克兰战争，俄罗斯总统弗拉基米尔·普京将攻击其他国家，同时他试图说服美国批准对基辅的进一步援助。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-12/duda-warns-putin-will-attack-others-if-russia-wins-in-ukraine</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 12 Mar 2024 21:53:04 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>乌克兰准备改革计划以释放欧盟500亿欧元援助</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-12/ukraine-readies-reform-plan-to-unlock-50-billion-of-eu-aid</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，乌克兰计划最早于下周提交一项提案，实施一系列改革和投资，以解锁欧盟最近承诺的 500 亿欧元（546 亿美元）援助计划中的大部分。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-12/ukraine-readies-reform-plan-to-unlock-50-billion-of-eu-aid</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 12 Mar 2024 21:23:37 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>寻求管理旧金山的科技投资者呼吁增加警察</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-12/san-francisco-mayoral-candidate-farrell-wants-police-and-tax-breaks-to-lure-tech</link>
      <description><![CDATA[旧金山市长的一位主要竞争者希望向警察提供更多资金并限制进入公园，这标志着该市激烈选举中严厉打击犯罪政策的最新转变。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-12/san-francisco-mayoral-candidate-farrell-wants-police-and-tax-breaks-to-lure-tech</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 12 Mar 2024 20:55:25 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>五角大楼取消了 25 亿美元英特尔拨款计划</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-12/pentagon-scraps-plan-to-spend-2-5-billion-on-intel-chip-grant</link>
      <description><![CDATA[知情人士称，五角大楼取消了一项花费高达 25 亿美元向英特尔公司提供芯片的计划，将责任转嫁给了另一个联邦机构——英特尔公司。商务部——以弥补不足。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-12/pentagon-scraps-plan-to-spend-2-5-billion-on-intel-chip-grant</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 12 Mar 2024 20:08:48 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>拜登赞扬波兰对乌克兰的援助，再次呼吁美国提供资金</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-12/poland-joins-czech-ammunition-plan-for-ukraine-sikorski-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[乔·拜登总统感谢访问白宫的波兰领导人在乌克兰战争的关键时刻向乌克兰提供的援助，并敦促美国议员批准更多资金，帮助基辅击退俄罗斯的入侵。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-12/poland-joins-czech-ammunition-plan-for-ukraine-sikorski-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 12 Mar 2024 14:06:21 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>澳大利亚称中国提议终止惩罚性葡萄酒关税</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-12/china-issues-draft-to-end-australia-wine-tariffs-winemaker-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[澳大利亚葡萄酒商和立法者表示，中国提议取消对该国葡萄酒的惩罚性关税，这表明随着两国寻求加强关系，为期三年的贸易争端即将结束。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-12/china-issues-draft-to-end-australia-wine-tariffs-winemaker-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 12 Mar 2024 09:39:17 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
